               <msContents>
                  <summary>Photocopy of twentieth-century manuscript</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="62v" facs="002"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1097Ammest">ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿmāda mǝśṭir</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>written entirely in Gǝ‘ǝz (it is usually written in Amharic and Gǝ‘ǝz). The basic work is an Amharic explanation of the teachings of the Church</note>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><locus from="2r" to="2v" facs="003"/><title>Introduction</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጽሒፈ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ርትዕት፡ ዘአወፈዩነ፡ አበዊነ፡ ቀደምት፡ ለአብዊነ፡ ዘአወፈይዎሙ፡ ሊቃውንት፡ ለሊቃውንትሂ፡ ዘአወፈይዎሙ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ለሐዋርያትሂ፡ ዘአወፈዮሙ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><locus from="2v" to="13r" facs="004"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1097Ammest#Trinity">ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿmāda mǝśṭir: Mystery of the Trinity ()</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3"><locus from="13v" to="45v" facs="015"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1097Ammest#Incarnation">ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿmāda mǝśṭir: Mystery of the Incarnation ()</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4"><locus from="45v" to="49v" facs="047"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1097Ammest#BaptismMystery">No item: LIT1097Ammest, could not check for BaptismMystery</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5"><locus from="49v" to="54v" facs="051"/><title>Mystery of Communion, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምሥጢረ፡ ቍርባን፡</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
